summary: A grand place to live in, nothing short of exquisite, the exterior of this mod features a private springlike bathing area, Beautiful entrance and outside dining area and a place for the servant to live, the interior features a library, armory, quarters, Dining area and a room with enchanting apparatus(for mages)
